If I understand your intention correctly, to populate dnd page with content on a development stage you may specify a default value for modules, like headings (value parameter)
<https://developers.HubSpot.com/docs/cms/building-blocks/modules/default-modules#header>
rich text (html parameter)
<https://developers.HubSpot.com/docs/cms/building-blocks/modules/default-modules#rich-text>
one line text (value parameter)
<https://developers.HubSpot.com/docs/cms/building-blocks/modules/default-modules#one-line-of-text>
image (img parameter with src field)
<https://developers.HubSpot.com/docs/cms/building-blocks/modules/default-modules#image>
